							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-900">Communication</h3>
						<p class="mt-4 text-base text-gray-500">In time of emergency if a donor face any problem in communication they can request for blood riders and blood riders will give them a ride towards there destination.</p>
					</div>
